description: NCAB Group AB engages in the manufacture, sale and supply of printed circuit boards (PCBs). The company is headquartered in Bromma, Stockholm and currently employs 488 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2018-06-05. The firm provides a full-service offer from design support to logistics solutions, with end-to-end accountability. The company purchases its products from a network of manufacturers, which are primarily located in China. Also, the Company conducts technical expertise and quality procedures. NCAB Holding AB supplies products to more than 40 markets and serves over 1500 customers.
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
name: NCAB Group AB (publ)
